TI  - Modelling Resilience: Extension and Community-Based Adaptation in Kenya and Zimbabwe
AU  - Munyaka, Jean-Claude Baraka
AU  - Abdem, Seyid Abdellahi Ebnou
AU  - Gallay, Olivier
AU  - Mutandwa, Edward
